high_descs: Go straight, then turn left and approach the counter to the right of the dishwasher, then turn right.
Pick up the knife on the counter, to the left of the lettuce.
Look up at the left cabinet above you.
Put the knife in the cabinet, on top of the plate.
Take the plate from the cabinet.
Look down and turn left to face the counter near the dishwasher.
Place the plate on the counter, to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife on a plate, on the counter.

high_descs: Walk across the room to the counter in the corner to the right of the dishwasher.
Pick up the butter knife on the counter that's closest to the corner.
Look up to the cabinet above.
Open the cabinet, stand the butter knife up on the blue plate.
Take the plate with the butter knife out of the cabinet, and close the cabinet.
Turn to the left towards the dishwasher.
Set the plate with the butter knife on it down on the counter above the dishwasher.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a butter knife on it on the counter above the dishwasher.

high_descs: Move across the room to the counter top with the lettuce and potato.  The counter top forms a corner here.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter.
Open the cupboard door on the right hand side above the counter.
Place the knife on the blue plate.
Pick up the plate and knife that are on the shelf. Close the cupboard door.
Turn around and move toward the counter top above the dishwasher.
Place the plate and knife on the  counter near the right side of the dishwasher.
anns.task_desc: Gather knife, plate to be placed in a different place on the counter.
